你這邊是想把原本超長的 JOIN 比對，改成用 ROW_NUMBER() 分組方式來做資料比對。
通常這樣做是為了避免：

* 重複資料造成 Cartesian 爆量
* 同樣內容多筆時 join 不準
* 想一筆一筆對應比對

可以改成這種寫法 👇

;WITH A_TABLE AS
(
    SELECT 
        groupid = ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY 
                ISNULL(TemplateId,0),
                ISNULL(GroupId,0),
                ISNULL(Parameter1,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter2,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter3,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter4,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter5,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter6,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter7,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter8,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter9,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter10,''),
                ISNULL(Score,0),
                ISNULL(CreatedDate,'19000101'),
                ISNULL(CreatedDate_UTC,'19000101'),
                ISNULL(LastModifiedDate,'19000101'),
                ISNULL(LastModifiedDate_UTC,'19000101'),
                ISNULL(CreatedBy,''),
                ISNULL(Enabled,0),
                ISNULL(Deleted,0),
                ISNULL(Repeatable,0),
                ISNULL(Category,''),
                ISNULL(LastModifedBy,''),
                ISNULL(qryId,0)
            ORDER BY qryId
        ),
        *
    FROM HRS_QuerySyntaxes
),
B_TABLE AS
(
    SELECT 
        groupid = ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY 
                ISNULL(TemplateId,0),
                ISNULL(GroupId,0),
                ISNULL(Parameter1,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter2,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter3,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter4,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter5,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter6,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter7,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter8,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter9,''),
                ISNULL(Parameter10,''),
                ISNULL(Score,0),
                ISNULL(CreatedDate,'19000101'),
                ISNULL(CreatedDate_UTC,'19000101'),
                ISNULL(LastModifiedDate,'19000101'),
                ISNULL(LastModifiedDate_UTC,'19000101'),
                ISNULL(CreatedBy,''),
                ISNULL(Enabled,0),
                ISNULL(Deleted,0),
                ISNULL(Repeatable,0),
                ISNULL(Category,''),
                ISNULL(LastModifedBy,''),
                ISNULL(qryId,0)
            ORDER BY qryId
        ),
        *
    FROM VERIFY..HRS_QuerySyntaxes
)
SELECT COUNT(*) AS HRS_QuerySyntaxes
FROM A_TABLE A
INNER JOIN B_TABLE B
    ON A.groupid = B.groupid
    AND ISNULL(A.TemplateId,0) = ISNULL(B.TemplateId,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.GroupId,0) = ISNULL(B.GroupId,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter1,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter1,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter2,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter2,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter3,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter3,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter4,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter4,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter5,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter5,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter6,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter6,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter7,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter7,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter8,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter8,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter9,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter9,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Parameter10,'') = ISNULL(B.Parameter10,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Score,0) = ISNULL(B.Score,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.CreatedDate,'19000101') = ISNULL(B.CreatedDate,'19000101')
    AND ISNULL(A.CreatedDate_UTC,'19000101') = ISNULL(B.CreatedDate_UTC,'19000101')
    AND ISNULL(A.LastModifiedDate,'19000101') = ISNULL(B.LastModifiedDate,'19000101')
    AND ISNULL(A.LastModifiedDate_UTC,'19000101') = ISNULL(B.LastModifiedDate_UTC,'19000101')
    AND ISNULL(A.CreatedBy,'') = ISNULL(B.CreatedBy,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.Enabled,0) = ISNULL(B.Enabled,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.Deleted,0) = ISNULL(B.Deleted,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.Repeatable,0) = ISNULL(B.Repeatable,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.Category,'') = ISNULL(B.Category,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.LastModifedBy,'') = ISNULL(B.LastModifedBy,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.qryId,0) = ISNULL(B.qryId,0);

這種寫法的核心像是在資料堆裡幫每組長得一模一樣的資料貼上流水號 🏷️
避免：

* A 有 2 筆
* B 有 2 筆
* join 後變 4 筆

這種「資料繁殖術」突然發生。